name: Sunnybrook Farm
summary: Sunnybrook Farm is a picturesque property with vast pastures, a cozy farmhouse, and a diverse range of livestock such as chickens, and an extensive vegetable garden.
description: Sunnybrook Farm is a charming rural property with sprawling pastures, a quaint farmhouse, and a variety of livestock. The farm is home to chickens, well-cared-for cows for dairy products, and sustainably-raised pigs for high-quality pork. The farm's extensive vegetable garden produces a bountiful harvest of fresh produce, used to feed the farm's inhabitants and sold at the local farmers market. It's a beautiful and sustainable property that celebrates the simplicity and beauty of rural life.

name: Wild Game Ranch Farm
summary: Wild Game Ranch is a farm that specializes in selling various types of meat, excluding beef. It offers a variety of wild game meats for customers to choose from.

location.address: 12971 Westheimer Rd, Houston, TX 77077, United States

description: Wild Game Ranch is a farm that specializes in selling a variety of meats, excluding beef. Their selection of wild game meats includes venison, elk, bison, wild boar, and rabbit, offering customers a unique and flavorful alternative to traditional meats. The farm operates with a focus on sustainability and animal welfare, ensuring that their animals are raised in natural environments with plenty of space to move and forage.

name: Harvest Fields Farm
summary: Harvest Fields Farm is a farm that specializes in producing fresh, high-quality produce. They sell their products directly to customers, offering a wide range of seasonal fruits and vegetables
description: Harvest Fields Farm is a family-owned farm that specializes in producing fresh and high-quality produce. They cultivate their fruits and vegetables with care, using sustainable and eco-friendly farming practices that prioritize the health of the soil, crops, and surrounding environment. The farm offers a wide range of seasonal produce that changes throughout the year, ensuring that customers always have access to the freshest and most flavorful products.

name: Green Pastures Ranch and Farm
summary: Green Pastures Ranch and Farm is a sustainable farm that offers both high-quality meat and fresh produce. They prioritize ethical and eco-friendly farming practices, providing customers with a unique and delicious farm-to-table experience.

location.description: George Bush Park/Eldridge, Houston, TX, USA

description: Green Pastures Ranch and Farm is a sustainable family-owned farm that offers a unique farm-to-table experience. The farm raises their animals, such as cows and pigs, in humane and natural environments without the use of hormones or antibiotics. They also grow a variety of fruits and vegetables using organic and sustainable farming practices

name: Heritage Harvest Farm and Ranch
summary: Heritage Harvest Farm and Ranch is a farm that produces high-quality meats and fresh produce using sustainable and eco-friendly farming practices.
description: Heritage Harvest Farm and Ranch is a family-owned and operated farm that produces high-quality meats and fresh produce using sustainable and eco-friendly farming practices. The farm is committed to providing customers with the freshest and most flavorful products while preserving the land for future generations.
